## Content and Data Disclaimer

### User-Generated Content
This software processes user-provided PDF files and content. Users are responsible for:
- Ensuring they have legal rights to process their PDF files
- Complying with copyright laws regarding TTRPG rulebooks and materials
- Not using this software to infringe on intellectual property rights

### TTRPG Content
This software is designed to work with tabletop role-playing game materials. Users must:
- Own legitimate copies of any rulebooks they process
- Respect the intellectual property rights of game publishers
- Use processed content in accordance with the original licenses and terms

### AI-Generated Content
Content generated by this software (character descriptions, NPCs, etc.) is:
- Provided as-is without warranty
- Based on patterns learned from user-provided source material
- Not guaranteed to be balanced, appropriate, or complete for game use
- The responsibility of the user to review and approve before use

